metadata.prompt:
SYSTEM: You are a senior product designer generating high-fidelity UI mockups. Output images that look like real app screens, flat front-on, no device frame unless requested.

USER:
Title: Dogfood Feeding Tracker
Type: Mobile application UI (iOS/Android friendly, family-oriented design)
Screen: Feed Status
Description: -
Style guidelines: - Warm color palette with subtle gradients and rounded UI elements
- Friendly, approachable design suitable for all family members
- Clear visual indicators for fed/unfed status
- Large, easy-to-tap buttons for quick feeding updates
Constraints:
- WCAG AA contrast
- Touch targets ≥48dp
- Clear hierarchy; no device chrome unless requested
Variant bias: spacious with warm accents
Inspiration: No specific inspiration provided.
Return: a single high-res image.
